caption.body: Our online database features a few gems from our collection of over a thousand safety information cards, including this Lufthansa German Airlines safety information card featuring the Airbus A380, the largest commercial passenger aircraft in service today. http://bit.ly/2ngcx2w  Image: Lufthansa German Airlines safety information card, Airbus A380-800, 2010. Gift of the William Hough Collection. 2011.123.131
